reviewText: I love Kath and Kim and I was surprised when I heard of this movie because I thought I'd seen all the episodes. Great little movie, and filled in some missing pieces! I can't wait to buy Kath and Kimderella! Love these ladies.
I can play this dvd on my new dvd player.  Just make sure you have or buy an all region dvd player.  Thank goodness, Now I can watch the real Kath & Kim.
